Package: bayesianquilts
Title: Adaptive Importance Sampling for Bayesian Cross-Validation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Joshua", "Chang", email = "josh@mederrata.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R port of the bayesianquilts library for interpretable Bayesian machine learning.
    Provides Adaptive Importance Sampling (AIS) methods for efficient Leave-One-Out (LOO)
    cross-validation, with support for brms models and custom likelihood functions.
